# GitHub Linguist overrides.
#
# The icon-preview HTML pages under assets/icon/ are generated design previews
# (~1.2 MB total) that are not part of the source. Left untouched they dominate
# GitHub's byte-counted language bar and mislabel this C++ project as "HTML".
# Mark them generated so Linguist excludes them from the language stats (and
# collapses them in diffs).
assets/icon/*.html linguist-generated=true
